create maven project skip archetype selection 
choose appropriate groupid,artifcatid
select pom in packaging


create a maven module give a name 
and in parent module choose the project created earlier



Create a Spring Boot Starter Project
Add Web,DataJpa,H2,lombok dependency
Copy the Invoice.java from spring_boot_jdbc_13
copy application.yml from spring_boot_jdbc_13
Add the JPA related annotation to Invoice.java
Create a Repository InvoiceRepository extending JpaRepository
Create a Service InvoiceService and Inject Invoice Repository use Constructor Injection
Access the Service from Main method and Test

